title: NO FEE - Great Location 2 BR near Halsey L Train
posting_body: ['Full Floor 2nd Level Apartment - 950 Square Feet of Space -  Best Price Per Square Foot', 'Clean and spacious apartment on the 2nd floor of a 3 family private house, minutes from restaurants and bars nearby.', ' On a quiet Tree-lined block,  Many original details, original floors, 10 ft ceilings, plaster moldings.', 'Apartment has 2 Bedroom', 'Living Room,', 'Dining Room,', 'Real Kitchen - with all Maple cabinets', 'Bathroom', 'New Windows in rear of Apartment', '1 block from subway at Halsey Street', 'Credit Check and Security Deposit required', 'Non Smokers - 1 small Cat allowed', "Near Great Restaurants - Fazio's - Houdini's - Nowadays Beer Garden- Queens Brewery - Red Note Rehearsal Studio - Broadway - Myrtle", 'Excellent Credit, Proof of Income Required and Employment History Required', 'Perfect for Singles, Couples - Not Ideal for roommates.', 'EMAIL me with your contact information and basic information  - The Apartment is Available By Appt only.', 'NO AGENTS PLEASE']
